<script type="text/javascript">
  
    function createExpanderRows(detailsUrl) {

        $(".bg_expanded").hide();

        $(".bg_row").mouseover(function() {
            $(this).attr('class', 'bg_row_roll');
        });

        $(".bg_row").mouseout(function() {
            $(this).attr('class', 'bg_row');
        });

        $(".bg_row").click(function(e) {

            var tr = document.getElementById("matchupDetails_" + $(this).attr("id"));

            if (tr.innerHTML == '') {
                //gets the content since it hasn't been loaded yet
                var contentText = $.ajax({

                    url: detailsUrl,
                    data: "eventId=" + $(this).attr("id"), // + eventId,
                    async: false

                }).responseText;

                $(tr).append(contentText);
            }
            $(tr).toggle();
        });

        // when links are clicked.. do not expand.
        $("a").click(function(event) {
            event.stopPropagation();

        });
    }

    function stopprop(e) 
    {
        if (!e) var e = window.event;
        e.cancelBubble = true;
        if (e.stopPropagation) e.stopPropagation();
    }  
</script>
